{"tid":1130534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"蝗婦慢行「拉龍」　途人嗌讓路反被罵？","createTime":"2019-04-29T06:16:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T07:14:00.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c094843396e1868e712a58ce66977a9edc1e1efc","tid":1130534,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:16:17.000Z","msg":"內地婦疑慢行「拉龍」 途人嗌讓路反被罵？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2VwFXhw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2VwFXhw&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9ajoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=ef01f59d\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2VwFXhw</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/photo/bkn-20190429134308938-0429_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190429141245\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190429%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190429134308938-0429_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190429141245&h=5b7fc98f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n退一步海闊天空。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n片段於星期六（27日）上傳至Facebook群組「上水人大聯盟」，只見當時港鐵上水站人來人往，戴帽的內地女子疑因玩手機，步速較慢，引起後方的途人不滿︰「一路行一路睇住個電話，成棚人跟住你，我話唔該你行快少少啫」。<br />\n<br />\n惟該內地女子認為途人可繞路而行，大聲喝斥途人態度欠佳︰「咩態度呀你，咁樣嘅人都有嘅！黐線㗎！」雖然當時有職員協助調停，但雙方情緒仍然激動。"},{"pid":"6d557d8d94e16926c62d2a87c759e765b3d3776b","tid":1130534,"uid":61795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:11:54.000Z","msg":"人太多<br />\n過多30年後<br />\n人口老化加劇<br />\n老人比例多左<br />\n阻街情況仲嚴重"},{"pid":"d1c1327ce14721f78d94418d04d897d39da2d230","tid":1130534,"uid":90020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T07:14:00.000Z","msg":"個途人都on9 一野撞開佢啦"}]}